'''Sandy's Sand Corp''' is a sand supplier{{CiteNPC|npc=Bert|quote=Sand! Lots o' sand! Me boss be Sandy o' Sandy's Sand Corp based in Brimhaven on the isle of Karamja an' I hauls sand fr' there to yon sand pit.|loc=The Hand in the Sand|name=Bert}} which owns many [[sand pit]]s found on [[Gielinor]], as well as the sand pit in [[Zanaris]]. The organisation is based in [[Brimhaven]] and is managed by [[Sandy]].{{NamedRef|Bert}} Employees work on rotas and are paid 50 [[coins]] every week, typically working 9 hour shifts.{{CiteNPC|npc=Sandy's rota|loc=The Hand in the Sand|quote=9am-6pm}} Their jobs including transporting sand from [[Karamja]] to top up their designated sand pits.{{NamedRef|Bert}}

==The Hand in the Sand==
Sandy had come into contact with [[Clarence]], a [[wizard]] from the [[Wizards' Guild]] and student of [[Zavistic Rarve]].{{CiteNPC|npc=Zavistic Rarve|loc=The Hand in the Sand|quote=Oh my! This is most definitely Clarence, my most able student!|name=Zarvistic}} He tasked Clarence with the creation of a spell which would make [[Bert]] believe anything he said, and in return offered to pay Clarence for this service.{{CiteNPC|npc=Sandy|loc=The Hand in the Sand|quote=[Why doesn't Bert remember the change in his hours?] Because.... because.... I bribed a wizard to put a spell on him so he would believe everything I say!!}} Sandy then changed Bert's rota,{{CiteNPC|npc=Sandy|loc=The Hand in the Sand|quote=[Why is Bert's rota different from the original?] Because... I changed it.}} and left the [[a magic scroll|scroll]] behind in Bert's house, intending to make Bert work longer without paying him more.{{CiteNPC|npc=Sandy|loc=The Hand in the Sand|quote=So that I could make him work longer without paying him more!}} Unwilling to pay Clarence, Sandy murdered him and hid his remains in various sand pits.{{CiteNPC|npc=Sandy|loc=The Hand in the Sand|quote=[What happened to the wizard?] I...I... I KILLED HIM! So I wouldn't have to pay him and no one would know. I put his body in the next load of sand.|name=Confession}} Eventually Bert uncovers a [[sandy hand|hand]] in the sand pit and enlists the [[player character|player]]'s help, starting [[The Hand in the Sand]] [[quest]].

==Members==
*[[Sandy]] - The owner and founder of the corp, currently ''missing''.
*[[Bert]] - A worker based in [[Yanille]].
*[[Mazion]] - A worker based on [[Entrana]].
*[[Blaec]] - A worker based in [[Zanaris]]. ''(presumably)''
*[[Reeso]] - A worker based in [[Rellekka]]. ''(presumably)''

==Trivia==
*The sand pits found in [[Dorgesh-Kaan]] and [[Prifddinas]] have no owners.

